{"question": "{"scenario": "", "healthText": "What is the best deworming medicine to be prescribed for this child ", "difficulty": "Medium", "language": "Pidgin", "userId": "", "topic": ""}", "answer": "What is the best deworming medicine to be prescribed for this child 

There are different types of worms and different medications for each.
